&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dispatch Installers:&lt;/strong&gt; Assign technicians to scheduled installations and ensure efficient route planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Sales Paperwork:&lt;/strong&gt; Handle all paperwork related to sales, ensuring that documentation is complete and accurate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage Installation Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee the installation calendar to ensure timely, well-coordinated service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Create &amp;amp; Manage Job Folders:&lt;/strong&gt; Organize job folders, including all necessary documentation for each installation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculate Task Pay:&lt;/strong&gt; Accurately calculate and track task pay for installers based on job completion and company policy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assist with Scheduling City Inspections:&lt;/strong&gt; Work with customers to schedule necessary city inspections for HVAC installations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coordinate Permits &amp;amp; Government Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with our 3rd-party permit/HERS company to meet all local regulatory requirements, minimizing customer impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coordinate with Subcontractors:&lt;/strong&gt; Arrange for crane services or any additional work needed for installations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Review Equipment Inventory:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor and track inventory levels to ensure necessary equipment is available for scheduled installations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assist with Payment Collection:&lt;/strong&gt; Support the accounting team in collecting payments from clients, ensuring all financials are processed in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Department Coordination:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with sales personnel, warehouse, accounting, and other internal teams to ensure smooth project workflow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Duties:&lt;/strong&gt; Perform any other tasks as assigned to help the team succeed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
